__package__.yml.rawContents:
types:
  GetExampleResponseMessage:
    properties:
      message: optional<string>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
    inline: true
  GetExampleResponse:
    discriminated: false
    union:
      - Schema
      - GetExampleResponseMessage
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  String:
    type: string
    validation:
      pattern: ^[a-zA-Z0-9]*$
      minLength: 3
      maxLength: 10
  Schema:
    properties:
      id:
        type: optional<integer>
        docs: The unique ID of the type.
        default: 50
        validation:
          min: 10
          max: 100
          exclusiveMin: true
          exclusiveMax: false
          multipleOf: 10
      age:
        type: optional<integer>
        docs: The age of the type.
        default: 50
        validation:
          exclusiveMin: true
          exclusiveMax: false
          multipleOf: 10
      name:
        type: optional<string>
        docs: The unique name of the type.
        default: type
        validation:
          pattern: ^[a-zA-Z0-9]*$
          minLength: 3
          maxLength: 10
      value:
        type: optional<double>
        docs: The value of the type.
        default: 1.1
        validation:
          min: 1.1
          max: 2.2
          multipleOf: 1.1
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
service:
  auth: false
  base-path: ''
  endpoints:
    defaultAndValidationRules:
      path: /example
      method: GET
      auth: false
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      display-name: Default and validation rules
      response:
        docs: Successful response
        type: GetExampleResponse
      examples:
        - response:
            body: {}
  source:
    openapi: ../openapi.yml

rootApiFile.rawContents:
name: api
error-discrimination:
  strategy: status-code
display-name: Sample API
